'''加雷斯·爱德华'''（{{lang-en|Gareth Edwards}}，{{bd|1975年|6月1日}}）是一名[[英国|英国]]电影导演，2010年的[[独立电影|独立电影]]《{{tsl|en|Monsters (2010 film)|異獸禁區}}》让他获得广泛关注<ref>{{cite web |first=Cath |last=Clarke |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2010/sep/23/first-sight-gareth-edwards |title=First sight: Gareth Edwards |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2010-09-23 |accessdate=2011-01-04 |archive-date=2013-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130506192206/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2010/sep/23/first-sight-gareth-edwards }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Laura |last=Davis |url=http://blogs.independent.co.uk/2010/12/02/interview-with-gareth-edwards-the-director-of-%E2%80%98monsters%E2%80%99/ |title=Interview with Gareth Edwards, the Director of ‘Monsters’ |work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] |date=2010-12-02 |accessdate=2011-01-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211142236/http://blogs.independent.co.uk/2010/12/02/interview-with-gareth-edwards-the-director-of-%E2%80%98monsters%E2%80%99/ |archivedate=2010-12-11 }}</ref>。知名作品为2014年科幻灾难片《[[哥斯拉_(2014年电影)|哥斯拉]]》，以及2016年全球票房达到10.5亿美元的《[[星際大戰外傳：俠盜一號|星際大戰外傳：俠盜一號]]》。

== 生平 ==
自童年时期他就对电影产生兴趣，《[[星球大战IV：新希望|星球大战]]》对他产生了极大的影响<ref>{{cite web |first=Jessica |last=Hopkins |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/feb/27/gareth-edwards-monsters-star-wars |title=The film that changed my life: Gareth Edwards |work=[[The_Observer|The Observer]] |date=2011-02-27 |accessdate=2011-11-17 |archive-date=2011-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110305193044/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/feb/27/gareth-edwards-monsters-star-wars }}</ref>。

1996年毕业于 University for the Creative Arts (UCA) 电影制作专业。2012年获得该校的荣誉博士学位<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ucreative.ac.uk/news/2012/july/honorary-degrees-2012#.U3MtXvldWyg |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-05-19 |archive-date=2014-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519114152/http://www.ucreative.ac.uk/news/2012/july/honorary-degrees-2012#.U3MtXvldWyg }}</ref>。

